ygData.msgSnippet: Hmmm As a DE necromancer, I was KOS, it took approximately 2 weeks of killing orcs to raise my faction to indifferent and now I can pass with impunity. As for
ygData.messageBody:
Hmmm

As a DE necromancer, I was KOS, it took approximately 2 weeks of killing
orcs to raise my faction to indifferent and now I can pass with impunity.
As for hunting in the keep, I have little exp there but from what I have
heard, I believe you are of too high a level to get much out of it.
Certainly nothing in the pass will give you experience. Hope that helps.

Grymspine
Lvl 30
Mithaniel Marr
